In Human Resources Setup it is possible to specify causes of absence and define precise units of measurement for the specific causes of absence:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000820-0/setup eng5.png"><br>

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000820-0/setup eng6.png"><br>

The causes of absence are defined in the table and it is possible to associate them with:

* specific units of measurement - unless otherwise specified, absences are recorded in the basic unit of measurement

* the color that highlights absences in Outlook calendar
